{
  "id": "adv_card_szk_08_01",
  "title": "兵藤雫 1話 野生に目覚めたアイドル",
  "script": [
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_office-01-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "env_adv_3d_office-01-000-noon",
      "startTime": 0
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": null,
      "speakerName": "",
      "speakerNameEn": "",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "――サニピの無人島ロケより少し前",
      "translations": {
        "en": "――A little before Sunny Peace's deserted island shoot",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 0,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_08_01/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_08_01-koh001.m4a",
      "text": "雫、無人島ロケの日が迫ってるけど、準備は順調か？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Shizuku‚ the deserted island shoot is approaching. Are preparations going smoothly?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 2.2666664958,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "speakerNameEn": "Shizuku",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_08_01/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_08_01-szk001.m4a",
      "text": "準備は……バッチリ。議論に議論を重ねて\nそれぞれ必要なものを選んだから……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Preparations are… perfect. After much discussion and deliberation‚\nwe each chose what we needed…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 11.3333331625,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_08_01/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_08_01-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "そうか、みんなで力を合わせて頑張ってるんだな\nそれは何よりだが……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I see‚ everyone's working together and doing their best.\nThat's good above all‚ but…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 18.6333331625,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "speakerNameEn": "Shizuku",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_08_01/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_08_01-szk002.m4a",
      "text": "{user}さん……？\nなんだか浮かない顔……どうかしたの？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "{user}-san…?\nYou look a bit down… what's wrong?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 23.1999998291,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_08_01/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_08_01-koh003.m4a",
      "text": "今回はサニピのみんなが熱望したから\nオファーを受けたが……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "This time everyone in Sunny Peace was eager for it‚\nso I accepted the offer‚ but…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 29.5999988119,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_08_01/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_08_01-koh004.m4a",
      "text": "脱出成功率1パーセントなんて数字を聞くと\nどうしても心配してしまうんだよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "When I hear numbers like a 1 percent escape success rate‚\nI can't help but worry.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 35.1999988119,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "speakerNameEn": "Shizuku",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_08_01/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_08_01-szk003.m4a",
      "text": "……ありがとう、{user}さん",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…Thank you‚ {user}-san.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 37.8000009496,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "speakerNameEn": "Shizuku",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_08_01/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_08_01-szk004.m4a",
      "text": "そんな風に心配してくれる人がいるから……\n私達も、無茶はしないようにしようって思える",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Because there's someone who worries about us like that…\nIt makes us feel like we shouldn't do anything reckless either.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 43.3999998291,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "speakerNameEn": "Shizuku",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_08_01/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_08_01-szk005.m4a",
      "text": "{user}さんはほんとに心強い……\nさすがは星見プロの……お父さん？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "{user}-san is really reassuring…\nAs expected of Hoshimi Pro's… father?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 50.7999998291,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_08_01/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_08_01-koh005.m4a",
      "text": "その言い方は語弊しかないが……\nマネージャーとしてついていてやれないのは心苦しいよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "That’s just a misleading way to put it…\nAs a manager‚ it pains me that I can't go with you.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 57.9666664958,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "speakerNameEn": "Shizuku",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_08_01/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_08_01-szk006.m4a",
      "text": "大丈夫……\nみんなで力を合わせて、ちゃんと帰って来るから……！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It's okay…\nWe'll work together and come back safe…!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 62.9333331625,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "speakerNameEn": "Shizuku",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_08_01/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_08_01-szk007.m4a",
      "text": "さくらちゃんはみんなを元気に引っ張ってくれるし\n怜ちゃんは冷静な判断が得意……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Sakura-chan energetically leads everyone‚\nRei-chan is good at calm judgment…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 70.6999998291,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "speakerNameEn": "Shizuku",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_08_01/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_08_01-szk008.m4a",
      "text": "遙子さんはキャンプ経験が頼りになるし、千紗ちゃんは\n癒しと、暗い茂みにもビビらない勇気担当……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Haruko-san's camping experience is reliable‚ and Chisa-chan is in charge of\nhealing and the courage to not be scared of dark thickets…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 78.7333331625,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_08_01/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_08_01-koh006.m4a",
      "text": "その流れでいくと、雫はなんの担当なんだ？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Following that flow‚ what are you in charge of‚ Shizuku?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 83.1666719396,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "speakerNameEn": "Shizuku",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_08_01/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_08_01-szk009.m4a",
      "text": "私は……みんなのオフショ担当……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I'm… in charge of everyone's off-shots…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 87.300005273,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "speakerNameEn": "Shizuku",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_08_01/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_08_01-szk010.m4a",
      "text": "公式のカメラでは決して捉えることの出来ない\nみんなの魅力を届ける……！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I'll deliver everyone's charm that can never be captured\nby official cameras…!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 95.1666664958,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_08_01/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_08_01-koh007.m4a",
      "text": "雫はブレないなぁ……。とにかくまずは安全第一だ\nみんな無事に帰って来てくれ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Shizuku‚ you never waver… Anyway‚ safety first.\nPlease all come back safely.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 103.1666664958,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "speakerNameEn": "Shizuku",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_08_01/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_08_01-szk011.m4a",
      "text": "分かった……ありがとう\nお土産話、楽しみにしてて",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I understand… thank you.\nLook forward to the souvenir stories.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 107.4666664958,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "speakerNameEn": "Shizuku",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_08_01/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_08_01-szk012.m4a",
      "text": "……あ。話だけじゃなくて、お土産……\n持って帰れるかも？　ココナッツとか……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…Ah. Not just stories‚ but actual souvenirs…\nMaybe I can bring some back? Like coconuts…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 113.5666649699,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_08_01/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_08_01-koh008.m4a",
      "text": "もらっても、ちょっと困りそうだな……\nお土産は無理に考えなくていいよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Even if you gave me some‚ I'd be a bit troubled…\nYou don't need to force yourself to think of souvenirs.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 119.9000125448,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": null,
      "speakerName": "",
      "speakerNameEn": "",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "――無人島ロケ終了後",
      "translations": {
        "en": "――After the deserted island shoot ended",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 123.9333621542,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_office-01-evening.webp",
      "bgName": "env_adv_3d_office-01-000-evening",
      "startTime": 125.1000181397
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_08_01/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_08_01-koh009.m4a",
      "text": "みんな無事に帰って来てくれて良かったよ\nサバイバル生活はどうだった？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I'm glad everyone came back safely.\nHow was the survival life?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 129.1666781942,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "speakerNameEn": "Shizuku",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_08_01/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_08_01-szk013.m4a",
      "text": "とっても楽しかった……とっても……！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It was so much fun… so much…!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 131.1333538652,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "speakerNameEn": "Shizuku",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_08_01/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_08_01-szk014.m4a",
      "text": "スマホやネットが恋しい時もあったけど、こうして思い\n返すと、サバイバル生活でしか得られない喜びがあった",
      "translations": {
        "en": "There were times I missed my phone and the internet‚ but looking back now‚\nthere was joy that could only be gained from survival life.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 138.1000115275,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "speakerNameEn": "Shizuku",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_08_01/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_08_01-szk015.m4a",
      "text": "二泊三日、四十八時間のサバイバル生活はハードだった\nけど……いろんなことを学べた気がする……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "The three days‚ two nights‚ 48-hour survival life was hard‚\nbut… I feel like I learned many things…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 147.6000115275,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "speakerNameEn": "Shizuku",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_08_01/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_08_01-szk016.m4a",
      "text": "五人で力を合わせて、自給自足生活を乗り切って……\n自分達でいかだも作った……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "The five of us worked together to get through self-sufficient living…\nWe even made a raft ourselves…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 155.6666781942,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "speakerNameEn": "Shizuku",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_08_01/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_08_01-szk017.m4a",
      "text": "今の私達は内なる野生に目覚めたアイドル……\nもう怖いものはない……！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Now we're idols who have awakened to the wild within…\nThere's nothing to fear anymore…!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 162.8000145793,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_08_01/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_08_01-koh010.m4a",
      "text": "う、内なる野生……？\nまぁ、絆が深まったならいいんだが……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "W-Wild within…?\nWell‚ if your bonds deepened‚ that's good‚ but…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 167.666681246,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "speakerNameEn": "Shizuku",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_08_01/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_08_01-szk018.m4a",
      "text": "ライブの演出まで次々浮かんで来る……\n自作のいかだに乗って登場とか……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Live performance ideas keep coming to mind…\nLike appearing on a handmade raft…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 174.366681246,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "speakerNameEn": "Shizuku",
