      "text": "ちなみに火起こしは、きりもみ式よりも\n弓ぎり式の方が手が痛くならなくていい",
      "translations": {
        "en": "By the way‚ for fire-making‚ the bow drill method\nis better than the hand drill method because your hands don't hurt.",
